; Rollup ships ~20 per-platform optional binaries (one per OS/arch/libc
; combination); pnpm checks every one against minimum-release-age even
; though only the host's binary ever installs. Excluding the family
; lets fresh installs proceed without loosening the global maturity
; policy. The host binary itself is still pinned via the lockfile.
minimum-release-age-exclude=@rollup/rollup-*
